 results suggest that the dimensions of spongy-layer elements are critical to colour production, but that {UV}-blue coloration can also be modified by the cortex and the thickness of the spongy layer. © 2005 The Linnean Society of London,Biological Journal of the Linnean Society, 2005,84, 259–271. [{ABSTRACT} {FROM} {AUTHOR}]
